      <span class="animate-fade-up inline-block text-prof-red text-sm font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-6" style="font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif;">
        Griffith University
      </span>

      <h1 class="animate-fade-up-1 text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl text-white leading-[0.95] mb-8" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-weight: 800;">
        We're the people<br>
        <span class="italic text-prof-red">who build things.</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="animate-fade-up-2 text-gray-400 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-xl leading-relaxed mb-10" style="font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif;">
