      </p>

      <div class="animate-fade-up-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start gap-4">
        <a href="#join" class="bg-prof-red hover:bg-red-700 text-white font-semibold px-7 py-3.5 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-red-500/20 text-sm" style="font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif;">
          Join our Discord
        </a>
        <a href="#about" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white font-medium px-7 py-3.5 transition-colors duration-300 text-sm flex items-center gap-2" style="font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif;">
