<%# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
    FAQ — CSS-only accordion
    ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ %>
<section id="faq" class="py-24 md:py-32">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal">
      <span class="text-prof-red text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase block mb-4" style="font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif;">FAQ</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl text-prof-text leading-tight" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-weight: 700;">
        Common questions
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <details class="reveal group border border-prof-border rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:border-prof-red/30 transition-colors duration-200">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer">
          <span class="text-prof-text font-semibold pr-4" style="font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif;">Do I need to be studying IT to join?</span>
          <svg class="faq-chevron w-5 h-5 text-prof-muted flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m19.5 8.25-7.5 7.5-7.5-7.5"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer px-6 pb-6 -mt-2">
          <p class="text-prof-secondary leading-relaxed" style="font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif;">
            No! We welcome students from all degrees. Many of our members study business, design, science, and other fields. If you're interested in technology, you belong here.
          </p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="reveal group border border-prof-border rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:border-prof-red/30 transition-colors duration-200">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer">
          <span class="text-prof-text font-semibold pr-4" style="font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif;">Does it cost anything to join?</span>
          <svg class="faq-chevron w-5 h-5 text-prof-muted flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m19.5 8.25-7.5 7.5-7.5-7.5"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer px-6 pb-6 -mt-2">
          <p class="text-prof-secondary leading-relaxed" style="font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif;">
            Nope. Membership is completely free. Most of our events are also free, including food and drinks. Some special events may have a small ticket price.
          </p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="reveal group border border-prof-border rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:border-prof-red/30 transition-colors duration-200">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer">
          <span class="text-prof-text font-semibold pr-4" style="font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif;">I'm a complete beginner. Will I fit in?</span>
          <svg class="faq-chevron w-5 h-5 text-prof-muted flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m19.5 8.25-7.5 7.5-7.5-7.5"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer px-6 pb-6 -mt-2">
          <p class="text-prof-secondary leading-relaxed" style="font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif;">
            Absolutely. Most of our members started with zero coding experience. Our workshops are designed for beginners, and our community is genuinely welcoming. Come to a Tech & Chill — the barrier to entry is literally "walk through the door."
          </p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="reveal group border border-prof-border rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:border-prof-red/30 transition-colors duration-200">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer">
          <span class="text-prof-text font-semibold pr-4" style="font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif;">Which campus are you on?</span>
          <svg class="faq-chevron w-5 h-5 text-prof-muted flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m19.5 8.25-7.5 7.5-7.5-7.5"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer px-6 pb-6 -mt-2">
          <p class="text-prof-secondary leading-relaxed" style="font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif;">
            Both Nathan (Brisbane) and Gold Coast. Most events run at Nathan with some replicated on the Gold Coast. Our Discord is the main hub regardless of campus.
          </p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="reveal group border border-prof-border rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:border-prof-red/30 transition-colors duration-200">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer">
          <span class="text-prof-text font-semibold pr-4" style="font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif;">How do I officially join?</span>
          <svg class="faq-chevron w-5 h-5 text-prof-muted flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m19.5 8.25-7.5 7.5-7.5-7.5"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer px-6 pb-6 -mt-2">
          <p class="text-prof-secondary leading-relaxed" style="font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif;">
            Jump into our Discord — that's the quickest way to get involved. For official Griffith membership, sign up on CampusGroups. But honestly, just show up to an event and you're in.
          </p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="reveal group border border-prof-border rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:border-prof-red/30 transition-colors duration-200">
        <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer">
          <span class="text-prof-text font-semibold pr-4" style="font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif;">Can I join the committee?</span>
          <svg class="faq-chevron w-5 h-5 text-prof-muted flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m19.5 8.25-7.5 7.5-7.5-7.5"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer px-6 pb-6 -mt-2">
          <p class="text-prof-secondary leading-relaxed" style="font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif;">
            Yes! Committee elections happen annually. We also take on general committee members and volunteers throughout the year. Reach out on Discord if you're interested — we're always looking for passionate people.
          </p>
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

